<paragraph id="FCA67BE00C38FE1E1D10157A57C3687D" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Portugiesisches Quellkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="E1DA9F75CCCB30833610D46229DE345C" pageId="null" pageNumber="770" type="description">
<paragraph id="5245737ED20F839BC3419D587064B5AB" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
Ausdauernd (?), schlaff, niederliegend oder aufsteigend, oft im Wasser flutend, bis 20 cm lang. 
<normalizedToken id="2D32FB28D349754782C76A737A111C4B" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="B1D5EFDDC465FD75CF9E0C7ACEAC33FF" originalValue="spatelförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">spatelfoermig</normalizedToken>
, bis 3 cm lang. 
<normalizedToken id="89354B020C9C7F71EF7DEC74FD375533" originalValue="Blütenstände" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Bluetenstaende</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="BDF01FBF8F182D3585FCA4A339D76BC4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Montiaceae" genus="Montia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="770" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fontana">
<emphasis id="FA7941398758B4EF26441185EEC9FD3D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">M. fontana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1). Reifer Same rundlich, Durchmesser 1-1,3 mm, bei 10facher 
<normalizedToken id="11B59BE4F83F252C1BD5498BB5063000" originalValue="Vergrößerung" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Vergroesserung</normalizedToken>
erscheint 
<normalizedToken id="A93B9AC5921A505E4A2540936262B53D" originalValue="Oberfläche" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Oberflaeche</normalizedToken>
nur 
<emphasis id="D7836BCC81099CA57233BA5CFC521FC6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
im Zentrum glatt, 
<normalizedToken id="ABBF78AE8A8E191B44409586679DA20A" originalValue="glänzend" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">glaenzend</normalizedToken>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E040F3D23E32E60C635166D19EAA65D4" authority="den Rand" authorityName="den Rand" family="Chenopodiaceae" genus="Blueten" pageId="null" pageNumber="770" rank="species" species="gegen">gegen den Rand</taxonomicName>
hin mit schmalen, am Grunde 
<normalizedToken id="6BA0EB42C28C79CEE72CD29E1136B099" originalValue="plötzlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">ploetzlich</normalizedToken>
verbreiterten, stumpfen, ca. 15 
<normalizedToken id="4000EDB7F509102AF8EF1102918ACF6B" originalValue="μ" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">μ</normalizedToken>
hohen Kegeln, die mit 
<normalizedToken id="4B21F029284E9E87DD808EE1DC9455DD" originalValue="körnigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">koernigen</normalizedToken>
Papillen besetzt sind
</emphasis>
(100fache 
<normalizedToken id="B52CCC85CA0FFB55205BACCC5B7E9372" originalValue="Vergrößerung" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Vergroesserung</normalizedToken>
notwendig). - 
<normalizedToken id="6F6364629EB28351989932BD36914364" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5F182CE20E236BB2B12A2DD9328862D7" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
<emphasis id="D49CAB1F32981C54B49093C81AAAC9C6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="891032BDF7496170DBAD355EAB479B3F" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
<emphasis id="113A0A8D9A490074866240A10972E1C7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Standort.</emphasis>
Keine 
<normalizedToken id="8ED5F5635200400D5412D064D605B4E8" originalValue="zuverlässigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">zuverlaessigen</normalizedToken>
Angaben, wahrscheinlich wie 
<emphasis id="6CFAFF77AC003F78C950CDFAD367154B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
<taxonomicName id="1F935AFD782E8D9FCF3FB7CBE68944E4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Montiaceae" genus="Montia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="770" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fontana">M. fontana</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="30FC08D3B87B4CB2A073B5C4F512C109" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
<emphasis id="644504661AA2531FA65CC2E7C3C52C87" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
<pageBreakToken id="55BBAC2FF6A92730617E997F817D67FD" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Verbreitung</pageBreakToken>
</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="CE942A70AA2366B5B6127DBD1C5BCF20" originalValue="ungenügend" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">ungenuegend</normalizedToken>
bekannt). Nach Walters (1953a) West-, Zentral- und 
<normalizedToken id="F40AB4086D622869DDBCF8AFD80011A7" originalValue="Südeuropa" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Suedeuropa</normalizedToken>
, Australien. - Im Gebiet nur im 
<normalizedToken id="95248D8B6D1D2911CE8513EEDCED66FB" originalValue="nördlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">noerdlichen</normalizedToken>
Teil: Material gesehen aus Vogesen (Nidegg), 
<normalizedToken id="1DFBE8FC083F22761E3DAC70A25FEC05" originalValue="Elsaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Elsass</normalizedToken>
(Zabern), Schwarzwald (Egg).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2255D8C98EDB7EBF48F601412548D299" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">
<emphasis id="04BBC6EAC47CB6CAC839B937D83BAA5C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Es 
<normalizedToken id="FA82194EB5530E85982338CD1962733C" originalValue="wäre" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">waere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="9065EEED22F20E6F9EA347B2C4DC59B9" originalValue="möglich" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">moeglich</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="DEA32B23EA910DBEE858B3D02B25F5AB" originalValue="daß" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">dass</normalizedToken>
es sich bei 
<taxonomicName id="CEC557414C265CCAD5F9D5C64C4AA43D" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Montiaceae" genus="Montia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="770" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lusitanica">
<emphasis id="30733C66E6AA23C5242E9920BA1E1E43" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">M. lusitanica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
um einen Bastard zwischen 
<taxonomicName id="DE137A0B936BD5DE2F3EF0BFECBBBC2E" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Montiaceae" genus="Montia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="770" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fontana">
<emphasis id="DD01C7E707472D54F30A6E4B25EBF141" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">M. fontana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="38A30402461701170F2E0996395767C5" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Montiaceae" genus="Montia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="770" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="verna">
<emphasis id="52B7A82581C8E8F88645034EB08FD05E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">M. verna</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
handelt, doch gibt es 
<normalizedToken id="8681C3FFF3CE919606A33464CB50E6C9" originalValue="darüber" pageId="null" pageNumber="770">darueber</normalizedToken>
keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
